• Your Neighborhood Grocery Store
• Fearless-ly featuring products, recipes & more...

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Trader Joe's on August 30, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text:
🌀We sell a lot of #brioche in our stores—and you might say that #challah is like braided brioche. (Granted, #TraderJoes Holiday Challah is more like the spiral hairstyle of a certain space princess.) The presence of eggs and sugar in both recipes is the connection, while the main difference is the use of oil (instead of butter) in the Challah.
•
Ultimately, the baked result is very similar: yellow-hued crumb that is soft, moist, and mildly sweet. Whether you’re enjoying it as part of your religious tradition—or simply because you can’t get enough of the ‘bread-just-short-of-cake’ profile—we’ve got your #loaves. Find them on our #bakery shelves for a limited time in September!
—
• 20 oz. Spiral Loaf • Kosher (pareve) • Limited •

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Trader Joe's on August 27, 2021. May be an image of fruit and indoor.

node.text:
🥯 #TraderJoes Vegan Cream Cheese Alternative makes the joy of a toasted bagel & schmear reality for the #dairyfree crowd. And while its name may be more practical than inspired—the character of this #vegancheese is nothing, if not inspired!
•
Our skilled supplier combines coconut oil, chickpea protein, and potato starch to create a base that looks, feels, and spreads like creamy cheese. The right amount of yeast extract and salt produces that lightly tart, #creamcheese flavor that lights up lactose lovers—while remaining #lactosefree.
•
Use it like regular cream cheese... on #bagels, of course, with or without some TJ’s #SmokedSalmon. Create a cream-cheese-like #frosting for cupcakes, or make an easy #vegandip by mixing it with your favorite TJ’s seasoning or hot sauce.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Trader Joe's on August 26, 2021. May be an image of succotash.

node.text:
📷: #TraderJoes Soyaki sauce with white fish on a bed of TJ’s Soycutash •
—
#Soyaki, as its name suggests, is our riff on #teriyaki sauce... and it’s a tasty riff! The base is soy sauce and cane sugar, with fresh garlic & ginger purées. But what really sets this sauce apart is the presence of sesame, both in the form of toasted sesame oil and #sesameseeds.
•
In addition to flavor, the seeds contribute a nice texture to this sweet & tangy sauce, setting it up for a variety of uses… It’s a ready #marinade for #grilledchicken or baked fish. How about Soyaki shrimp #stirfry? And since it’s #vegan, it’s well-matched with baked #tofu or roasted vegetables. It even makes a great #dippingsauce for any of the #Gyoza you find in our freezers!

node.text:
📷: #TraderJoes Organic Veggie Bites & TJ’s Tofu Scramble with Soy Chorizo wrapped in a tortilla •
—
Organic Veggie Bites are like Trader Potato Tots, except bigger… and with more #veggies! Each Bite is really about two bites. And instead of just potatoes, they’re made with a variety of organic #vegetables, including carrots, celery, onions, sweet potatoes, kale, broccoli, and tomatoes.
•
Organic brown rice flour helps hold things together, while a simple seasoning of salt & pepper enhances all the #vegetable flavors. And just like traditional tots, the cooked texture is crisp on the outside and soft in the middle—whether you cook them in a conventional oven, #airfryer, or stovetop skillet! #eatyourveggies
—
• Heat & Serve • Organic • Vegan • Gluten Free •
• Link in bio for price & more details •

node.text:
🥣 Do you want your cereal hot or cold? Creamy or crunchy? Simple or sweetened? Sound off in this #TraderJoes Spoon Off (a spin off of the traditional #TJsSnackOff)…
—
💙OVEN TOASTED OLD FASHIONED ORGANIC OATS: A cup of water, a dash of salt, and about five minutes on the stovetop (even less time in the microwave), yields a steaming, satisfying bowl of organic, oven toasted, whole #rolledoats. They’re a good source of fiber—and with unlimited enhancements from our shelves (raisins, almonds, maple syrup, cinnamon…), you can have a bowl for #breakfast every day and never get bored!
•
💛ALMOND BUTTER PUFFS: If your puffs aren’t puffy enough, your milk can become a cereal killer. Thankfully, the combination of #puffedrice and golden Ecuadorian #quinoa in these #glutenfree, pebble-y Puffs keeps them crunchy, even after the milk is poured! Roasted #almondbutter (40% of the recipe) flavors the crunch, along with a dolce dusting of powdered cocoa and sugar for a tasty breakfast that’s a cut above corn flakes.
—
👉🏼 Which TJ’s #cereal bowls you over: 💙 or 💛?

node.text:
📷: “Trailblazer Bites,” featuring #TraderJoes Raw Almonds • Link In Bio for #TJsRecipe •
—
Our one-pound bag of Raw Almonds is filled with Extra no.1 Nonpareil Almonds—the highest-grade almonds grown in California. (Indeed, “nonpareil” is French for “no equal.”) The state requires that #rawalmonds are either steam-pasteurized or fumigated with chemicals. Of course, we’ve taken the steam route, which yields the best tasting nuts.
•
Add the fact that these #Almonds don’t stay on our shelves very long—we sell so many—and you have a foolproof formula for the freshest, best-tasting almonds available… short of a personal visit to the almond farm!
•
👉🏾 What’s your favorite way to enjoy TJ’s Raw Almonds?
—
• Just Almonds • Grown In California’s Central Valley •

node.text:
Back to school and work means back to the scramble for a meaningful morning break that’s fast and full of what your body needs to tackle the day. Since you’re already scrambling, why not do the #TraderJoes Tofu Scramble? It’s a heat & eat #breakfast (3 to 4 microwave minutes), packed with #plantbased protein to propel you onward.
•
The 10 oz. bowl contains chunky scrambled #tofu, vegetables (including spinach and red & green bell peppers), savory #soychorizo, and vegan Cheddar-style shreds. In fact, the whole meal is #vegan, and #glutenfree. Each 370-calorie bowl is also delicious, and the stress-free kind of #scramble that will help start your day off right!
—
• 25g Protein Per 10 oz. Serving • Find it in our freezers •

node.text:
The best food substitutes are free of what you don’t want (or can’t have), while maintaining everything you do want—like an authentic appearance, pleasant texture, and great flavor. #TraderJoes Shredded Parmesan #Cheese Alternative lives up to this tough standard, to the glee of vegans and #dairyfree folks everywhere! 
•
It’s 100% #plantbased, with a combination of highly refined #coconutoil and modified potato starch uniting to recreate the shredded, hard-cheese texture of real #Parmesan. For flavor, yeast extract and salt are mixed to mimic the lightly sharp, nutty #umami that makes Parm such an excellent partner for #pastas, soups, salads, and #garlicbread.
•
👉🏼 Have you tried it? What do you think?
—
• 8 oz. Resealable Pouch • #LactoseFree • #Vegan • 
• In our refrigerated cheese case every day •

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Trader Joe's on August 18, 2021. May be an image of food and drink.

node.text:
📷: “Peach Rosé Sangria,” featuring #TraderJoes Petit Reserve Central Coast Rosé •
• Link in bio for #TJsRecipe and wine price •
—
This #roséwine comes to us from an iconic winery located in the #CentralCoast AVA, California. Simply put, they produced way too much of their award-winning rosé, so we made a deal to help them out (and us, and you), by taking some off their hands.
•
It’s delicious on its own, boasting a wonderful creaminess that extends through the long-lasting finish, with notes of wild strawberry, peach, and rhubarb. But it also has enough body to stand up to spicy fish tacos, or baked salmon with pesto & Parmesan.
•
And at about half of what you’d pay in their label (for the exact same #wine), an already lovely rosé becomes twice as nice!
—
• 750mL Bottle • Vegan • #WineWednesday •
👉🏾Available only at TJ’s where wine is sold 🍇

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Trader Joe's on August 17, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text:
🐿 #TraderJoes Crispy Peanut Butter Filled Milk Chocolate Peanuts are not just Milk Chocolate #PeanutButterCups in disguise—not that there’d be anything wrong with that! There’s a textural element going on here that fosters a unique eating encounter…
•
The same German confectioner that makes our Hot Cocoa Snowman has created for us a charming candy mold in the shape of a whole #peanut. The outer shell is made from high-quality #milkchocolate, while the center is filled with smooth #peanutbutter, dotted with crisped rice.
•
Between the raised detail on the peanut-shell, and the crisped-rice crunch, you’ll experience a multifaceted mouthfeel to complement the sweet-salty, #chocolate-peanut butter flavor. You’d be smart to squirrel away a bag or three!
—
• 4.94 oz. Resealable Pouch • About 13 Pieces •
• No Palm Oil • Product of Germany 🇩🇪•

node.text:
🎥: “Lessons In Lunch: 3 Salads, 3 Ingredients Each” • Link In Bio for Recipes & Full Video •
—
Here are three #lunchtime #salad recipes, each using just three #TraderJoes ingredients. They’re loaded with enough crunch & flavor to keep things exciting—and enough #plantbased protein to avoid the afternoon snack attack.
•
We even show you how to pack these #salads in advance using a mason jar with a lid, so you won’t end up with a soggy mess—whether you’re lunching on the quad, in the office, or at your kitchen table. Start taking notes, class is officially in session!
—
🥗 Visit youtube.com/traderjoes for more TJ’s recipes 👈🏻

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Trader Joe's on August 13, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text:
🧀 What’s better than the taste of one great #cheese? How about about the taste to two great cheeses, together in one! #TraderJoes Cheddar & Gruyere Mélange proves the greatness of such synergy…
•
It begins with milk from cows that graze in the rolling hills of northwestern Wisconsin. Certified Master Cheesemakers skillfully blend #Cheddar and #Gruyere styles to yield one, unique and stunning profile.
•
The texture approaches crumbly—but doesn’t quite make it all the way there—with a dual personality, mimicking the mildly sweet creaminess of Gruyere, mingled with the rich nuttiness of an aged Cheddar. It’s a Mélange that will enhance just about any eating scenario, from #burgers to #macandcheese to your preprandial glass of #wine!
—
• 8 oz. Cut Pieces (approx.) • Microbial Enzymes •
• Pasteurized • Aged 90 Days •
